  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients undergoing lumbar laminectomy surgery will receive either 5 or 10 mg melatonin or
      placebo once the evening before surgery and again 90 minutes before surgery. Pain and anxiety
      will be assessed over the 24 hour period following surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
